BOTH: (CHUCKLE)

38:29.724 --> 38:30.891
CHRISTOPHER: (EXHALES)

38:48.617 --> 38:49.785
Bon appétit.

38:50.911 --> 38:52.413
-Thank you.
-(CHUCKLES LIGHTLY)

38:53.789 --> 38:55.541
(SLURPING)

38:56.667 --> 38:58.085
-CHRISTOPHER: Mmm.
-(CHUCKLES)

38:58.169 --> 39:00.713
CHRISTOPHER: Mmm.
(SWALLOWS, SMACKS LIPS)

39:10.848 --> 39:12.683
Sorry, Chris. (INHALES SHAKILY)

39:15.186 --> 39:19.315
-Wh-- What's the matter?
