-It's all my fault. (SNIFFLES)
-Hey.

39:25.821 --> 39:30.076
-No, it's not, Susan.
-It is. (INHALES SHAKILY)

39:30.159 --> 39:32.912
It's not your fault.
Don't you ever think that.

39:32.995 --> 39:35.206
(INHALES SHAKILY)
I've ruined your life.

39:35.289 --> 39:37.541
-Oh! (CHUCKLES)
-(SOBS)

39:37.625 --> 39:40.002
You haven't ruined my life.

39:40.086 --> 39:44.131
-How can you say such a thing?
-(SOBS)

39:44.215 --> 39:45.716
(SNIFFLES)

39:45.800 --> 39:48.427
-Because...
-You are my life.

39:50.054 --> 39:52.348
You're my whole life.
You know that.

39:52.431 --> 39:55.226
(SNIFFLES, INHALES SHARPLY)

39:57.895 --> 40:00.564
-(INHALES SHARPLY)
-Come on, now.

40:00.648 --> 40:03.442
-(SNIFFLES)
-Everything's gonna be just...

40:03.526 --> 40:05.945
-fine.
-(BREATHES SHAKILY)

40:07.321 --> 40:09.198
Everything
is gonna be all right.

40:10.699 --> 40:11.909
Okay, baby?

40:13.661 --> 40:14.829
I promise.

40:17.540 --> 40:22.878
♪ (MELANCHOLIC MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

40:33.556 --> 40:36.308
♪ (MUSIC QUIETENS) ♪

40:36.392 --> 40:38.894
-(CRICKETS CHIRP)
-(DOG BARKS DISTANTLY)

40:39.979 --> 40:44.817
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

40:44.900 --> 40:51.782
♪ (SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

41:13.512 --> 41:17.057
♪ (SOMBER MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

42:00.518 --> 42:04.355
(CRACKLING)

42:11.320 --> 42:14.365
♪ (SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC
CONTINUES) ♪

42:22.873 --> 42:25.417
CHRISTOPHER: Dear DCI Collier,

42:25.501 --> 42:28.796
we note the growing notoriety
of your inquest

42:28.879 --> 42:32.216
and possible assumptions
about our involvement.

42:32.299 --> 42:34.134
We have, therefore,
decided to return

42:34.218 --> 42:36.136
to England immediately.

42:36.220 --> 42:37.429
We prefer this approach

42:37.513 --> 42:41.267
rather than to leave ourselves
open to a surprise arrest,

42:41.350 --> 42:44.144
since my wife is already
sufficiently frightened.

42:44.228 --> 42:46.772
-(KNOCKING, DOOR OPENS)
-Sorry to interrupt, but,

42:46.855 --> 42:49.525
uh, this just came in
from Christopher Edwards, sir.

42:50.567 --> 42:52.569
(DOOR SQUEAKS, CLOSES)

42:52.653 --> 42:53.988
-You, get me London.
-(TELEPHONE RINGS)

42:54.071 --> 42:56.031
-OFFICER: Yes, sir.
-(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

42:56.115 --> 42:58.784
-You, get me the
British Transport Police, ASAP.
-MACBRIDE: Yeah, on it, sir.

42:58.867 --> 43:02.746
-(TELEPHONE RINGS)
-Emma, where the fuck are ya?

43:02.830 --> 43:04.039
Later this evening,

43:04.123 --> 43:07.960
my wife and I
will board the Eurostar

43:08.043 --> 43:10.170
and surrender ourselves
to the authorities

43:10.254 --> 43:12.423
