are so pricey,

43:18.679 --> 43:20.139
and we find ourselves

43:20.222 --> 43:22.016
a bit short of funds
at the moment,

43:22.099 --> 43:24.810
could you be so kind
as to arrange tickets for us

43:24.893 --> 43:28.689
