saying, stick to the plan.

45:38.777 --> 45:42.030
That's right, darling.
Stick to the plan.

45:43.907 --> 45:45.451
How much money have you got?

45:46.410 --> 45:47.953
-Not much.
-How much?

45:48.996 --> 45:49.997
About...

45:50.956 --> 45:54.001
two euros something. (SIGHS)

45:56.378 --> 45:58.755
I've got one and a bit.
Hand it over.

46:00.632 --> 46:02.009
Might as well use it up!

46:06.096 --> 46:07.639
(CHUCKLES)

46:10.100 --> 46:12.019
COLLIER: Do you know
what I find weird, though?

46:12.102 --> 46:14.229
