46:21.487 --> 46:23.155
-(CHUCKLE)
-Do you know what I mean?

46:23.822 --> 46:25.282
(CHUCKLES)

46:25.365 --> 46:27.534
-Did you say something, Emma?
-What?

46:28.368 --> 46:29.578
No, just saying about

46:29.661 --> 46:31.497
those long scotch eggs.

46:31.580 --> 46:33.540
-Service stations.
-(CHUCKLES)

46:33.624 --> 46:35.417
Like, "Show me the chicken
that laid that."

46:35.501 --> 46:36.585
-WILKIE: (CHUCKLES)
-LANCING: (GRUNTS)

46:36.668 --> 46:38.545
-'Cause it's a weird egg.
-LANCING: Yeah.

46:38.629 --> 46:40.422
Fuck's sake. Is this thing on?

46:40.506 --> 46:43.008
♪ (LIVELY MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

46:43.091 --> 46:44.343
COLLIER: (GROANS)

46:47.763 --> 46:51.517
(INDISTINCT ANNOUNCEMENT
