47:17.793 --> 47:18.961
(CHUCKLES)

47:19.836 --> 47:25.884
♪ (LIVELY MUSIC CONTINUES) ♪

47:39.815 --> 47:41.984
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

47:43.694 --> 47:47.364
(SIRENS BLARE)

47:56.665 --> 47:59.376
