48:50.260 --> 48:53.180
♪ (MUSIC CALMS) ♪

48:54.431 --> 48:56.183
PATRICIA WYCHERLEY:
(SHOUTS) ...fucking saying.

48:56.266 --> 49:01.229
I am just spending a few seconds
alone with my own daughter.

49:01.313 --> 49:04.816
What do you need?
