49:04.900 --> 49:07.361
Go on, just get up
to your bedroom!

49:08.820 --> 49:11.114
♪ (LIVELY MUSIC PICKS UP) ♪

49:13.909 --> 49:15.327
Oh, Chris.

49:15.410 --> 49:18.747
CHRISTOPHER:
(BREATHES SHAKILY, SNIFFLES)

49:18.830 --> 49:21.333
It's all right.
