49:21.416 --> 49:24.336
I'm stronger than I look. (SOBS)

49:27.005 --> 49:29.257
Chris, I don't think
I can say goodbye to you.

49:30.550 --> 49:32.844
No one is saying goodbye,
my love.

49:34.971 --> 49:37.140
There are no goodbyes
between us.

49:39.309 --> 49:42.145
I'll never leave you.
You know that.

49:45.691 --> 49:46.692
Never.

49:52.072 --> 49:53.490
Give me your passport.

50:01.081 --> 50:02.290
Are you ready, darling?

50:03.667 --> 50:04.835
Suppose so.

50:12.843 --> 50:19.099
(SIRENS BLARE)

50:19.182 --> 50:21.143
(INDISTINCT CHATTER
OVER POLICE RADIO)

50:21.226 --> 50:23.353
-COLLIER: DCI Collier,
Nottingham Police.
