50:55.135 --> 50:57.971
You got eyes on them, Paul?
Over.

50:58.054 --> 51:00.182
SUSAN: Where did they say
to meet them?

51:00.265 --> 51:02.309
By the south-west...

51:02.392 --> 51:05.228
exit of the St. Pancras Hotel
car park,

51:05.312 --> 51:06.980
which I think is this way.

51:07.063 --> 51:08.106
COLLIER ON RADIO:
Paul, come in.

51:08.190 --> 51:09.900
Have you got eyes on them? Over.

51:09.983 --> 51:12.527
WILKIE: Not yet, sir,
but eyes peeled. Over.

51:12.611 --> 51:15.489
♪ (MUSIC CALMS, CONTINUES) ♪

51:17.199 --> 51:20.035
CHRISTOPHER: Sorry. Excuse me.
Terribly sorry.

51:20.118 --> 51:22.037
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

51:27.459 --> 51:29.169
I think I might
have spotted them, sir.

51:30.170 --> 51:31.797
What are they doing?

51:31.880 --> 51:34.549
They're just sort
of walking, sir.

51:34.633 --> 51:37.552
In your direction. Over.

51:37.636 --> 51:40.680
CHRISTOPHER: Remember,
one step at a time... (EXHALES)

51:40.764 --> 51:41.848
...like we said.

51:41.932 --> 51:44.726
They arrest us,
they read us our rights.

51:44.810 --> 51:46.728
We know what we're gonna say.
We've gone through it

51:46.812 --> 51:48.647
a thousand times
and we're ready.

51:48.730 --> 51:50.649
But don't say a word
without a solicitor.

51:50.732 --> 51:51.983
-Right?
-Yes.

51:52.067 --> 51:55.904
And remember, if you don't like
the first one they offer,

51:55.987 --> 51:58.657
ask to meet another.
You're in charge.

52:00.242 --> 52:01.493
Then come the police interviews.

52:01.576 --> 52:03.495
They'll try to confuse you,
but don't let them.

52:03.578 --> 52:07.207
Just tell our story,
simply and calmly.

52:07.290 --> 52:10.836
No need to make anything up.
Just tell them the truth.

52:10.919 --> 52:13.046
Yes, just tell them the truth.

52:13.129 --> 52:18.093
♪ (MUSIC INTENSIFIES) ♪

52:29.729 --> 52:33.900
♪ (MUSIC BUILDS TO CLIMAX) ♪

52:33.984 --> 52:35.318
Good evening.

52:38.363 --> 52:40.907
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

52:40.991 --> 52:42.534
♪ (DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

52:42.617 --> 52:44.536
REPORTER 1: Susan
and Christopher Edwards

52:44.619 --> 52:46.913
might have seemed
like an ordinary couple,

52:46.997 --> 52:49.791
but together, they had carried
a sinister secret

52:49.875 --> 52:51.710
for over fifteen years.

52:51.793 --> 52:53.086
REPORTER 2:
Buried in the rear garden

52:53.169 --> 52:55.505
of this unassuming
Mansfield property

52:55.589 --> 52:57.883
were the bodies
of Susan's parents.

52:57.966 --> 52:59.634
REPORTER 3: Remains found
last month are believed

52:59.718 --> 53:03.221
to be those of William
and Patricia Wycherley.

53:03.305 --> 53:04.598
REPORTER 4:
Buried in the back garden

53:04.681 --> 53:07.225
of a semi-detached house
at Forest Town in Mansfield.

53:07.309 --> 53:09.936
Following a tip-off,
police make a grim discovery.

53:10.020 --> 53:12.772
One woman said she knew
of an elderly couple

53:12.856 --> 53:14.357
who were here in the '90s.

53:14.441 --> 53:16.401
One day,
they just disappeared.

53:16.484 --> 53:19.571
Everyone assumed
that they'd emigrated,

53:19.654 --> 53:21.406
and no one thought
anything of it.

53:21.489 --> 53:23.408
REPORTER 5: A postmortem
examination revealed

53:23.491 --> 53:25.827
they'd both been shot twice
with a revolver

53:25.911 --> 53:27.203
similar to this one.

53:27.287 --> 53:29.581
In panic, the Edwards
fled to France

53:29.664 --> 53:32.208
before eventually contacting
police in the UK

53:32.292 --> 53:33.793
when they ran out of money.

53:35.003 --> 53:37.130
In an email,
Christopher Edwards wrote,

53:37.213 --> 53:38.715
"We're going
to surrender ourselves

53:38.798 --> 53:40.967
-to the UK authorities."
-(SIREN BLARES)

53:41.051 --> 53:43.511
REPORTER 6: Late last night,
at St. Pancras Station,

53:43.595 --> 53:46.264
husband and wife Susan
and Christopher Edwards...

53:46.348 --> 53:48.475
REPORTER 7: ...were arrested
on suspicion of murder...

53:48.558 --> 53:50.894
REPORTER 8: ...on their return
from France.

53:50.977 --> 53:52.187
REPORTER 9: They have since
been escorted

53:52.270 --> 53:53.438
back to Nottinghamshire,

53:53.521 --> 53:56.232
where they'll be held in custody
for the next 24 hours

53:56.316 --> 53:58.068
to be questioned by police.
